  * [DOCKER] docker-compose.yaml uses bind mount by default for easy config.yaml editing
  * [CI/CD] GitHub Actions updated to Node.js 24 runtime (node24); actions versions bumped
  * [TESTS] Added unit tests: replication worker, manager sync, credentials, SSRF, object adapter,
